title: Dishwasher Rinse Aid Cap
description: Dishwasher Rinse Aid Cap ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 15 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11755938 Manufacturer Part Number WPW10524919 This part holds the rinse aid liquid in the dispenser until the timer activates the rinse cycle.

installationInstructions.author: Kathryn from WINTERPORT, ME
installationInstructions.title: Rinse aid cap was melted when it came out of the designated spot and melted against the heat coil.
installationInstructions.content: Open the washer door, remove old rinse aid cap. Place new cap into designated spot, screw into place.
